# docx -> html

```sh
pandoc -s -o out.html in.docx
```

# md -> PDF

```sh
# Output PDF
pandoc in.md --pdf-engine=lualatex -o out.pdf

#To support Chinese, add the following lines at the beginning of in.md
# ---
# CJKmainfont: Noto Serif CJK SC
# CJKsansfont: Noto Sans CJK SC
# ...
```

# md -> man

```sh
# Beginning of the markdown file should be like:
#
# ---
# title: HELLO
# section: 1
# header: User Manual
# footer: hello 1.0.0
# date: January 13, 2021
# ---
#
pandoc -s -t man -o hello.1 hello.md
```

# bibliography

```sh
pandoc source.md --bibliography src.bib -s -o output.rtf
```
